STATE of North Carolina
v.
Olivia CHISHOLM No. 341P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 14, 2019 Paul F. Herzog, Attorney at Law, Fayetteville, for Chisholm, Olivia. Kathy M. McCraw, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Olivia Chisholm, for Chisholm, Olivia. R. Andrew Murray, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 9th of October 2018 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."
